🔷 Diagram (Understanding Flow)

```text
Timers → I/O → Poll → Check → Close
        ↑                     ↓
        └────── Event Loop ───┘
```

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 process.nextTick()

```javascript
process.nextTick(() => {
  console.log("Next Tick");
});
```

✔ Executes **before promises**

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 setImmediate()

```javascript
setImmediate(() => {
  console.log("Immediate");
});
```

✔ Runs in **check phase**

